<!DOCTYPE html>
  <html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>アプリ名</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900">

    <header class="bg-yellow-400 p-6 text-center text-2xl font-bold">
      アプリ名
    </header>

    <section class="text-center my-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">映えやいいねを気にせず自分の1人ディズニーの思い出を残すことができます</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="flex justify-center my-6">
      <img src="<%= asset_path('disney.jpg') %>" alt="ディズニーのイメージ" class="w-4/5 max-w-lg rounded-lg shadow-md">
    </section>

    <section class="text-center my-6">
      <p class="mb-2 text-lg">初めての方はこちらから</p>
      <%= link_to "新規登録", new_user_registration_path, class: "bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition" %>
    </section>

    <section class="text-center my-6">
      <p class="mb-2 text-lg">アカウントをお持ちの方はこちら</p>
      <%= link_to "ログイン", new_user_session_path, class: "bg-green-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:bg-green-700 transition" %>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white text-center p-4 mt-8"></footer>
  </body>
</html>